verbose_text: Moreover, in the engineered tendon, SCX reduced the expression of osteogenesis gene ALP, the transcription factor SOX9 which associated with chondrogenesis XREF_BIBR, and mesodermal related gene markers Snail1 and Snail2 XREF_BIBR (XREF_FIG).
